The '''Bakur Senatorial Academy''' was a four-year university in the [[Bakura/Legends|Bakuran]] capital of [[Salis D'aar/Legends|Salis D'aar]], aimed at preparing its students for service in the Bakuran government, especially the [[Bakuran Senate]].

The Senate elected its own replacements, and nepotism was an affirmed practice of the Bakuran government, so it can be assumed that the children of existing [[Senator/Legends|senators]] and ministers were sent to the Academy, or at least were given first choice in admission. At any rate, this was the case for the members of the [[Captison family]].

During the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] occupation of Bakura, graduates of the Academy were the sent to [[Coruscant/Legends|Imperial Center]] to do an additional year in postgraduate work, ensuring their indoctrination in Imperial political views.

